---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Data Use | SIR Saathi">
  <main class="shell content-page">
    <h1>Data Use</h1>
    <p>Electoral rolls are public documents, but bulk voter data can still create privacy and misuse risks.</p>
    <p>SIR Saathi does not support voter profiling, campaign targeting, caste or religion inference, or bulk exports.</p>
    <p>Any indexed search must be limited to voter self-service, source verification, and official-action guidance.</p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
